item.description: This Simple Trick Will Make Your Paper Airplane Fly for Miles - You Won’t Believe How Easy It Is! We all remember the childhood joy of folding paper airplanes and watching them sail through the air. But what if we told you that with a few simple steps you can make your paper airplane fly for miles? That’s right, you can make your paper airplane fly for miles with this easy trick.
